From 4c92ab9ecd5fd6f0b6c10ff0129339c37ce45b5a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Work Leaf Bench <bench@example.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 20:45:23 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] ADD reviewed-feature completion prompts to close finished
 chats

Select the patch-agent chat after review, append the feature-done yes/no prompt, and let the terminal hide or reopen that agent row locally so reviewed work can stay available for linearization without accidentally resuming the agent.
